==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Procreant
<hw>Pro"cre*ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>procreans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>procreare</ets>. See
<er>Procreate</er>.]</ety> <def>Generating; producing; productive;
fruitful; assisting in procreation.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧His
pendent bed and <xex>procreant</xex> cradle.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Procreant</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Procreant
<hw>Pro"cre*ant</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that which,
procreates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Procreate</ent>⟦br⟧
